\b0\fs32 \cf0 The bean will be fully covered with only the LED showing. The covering will be made of cardboard and will be available in two major designs : In the shape of a skull i.e. a phantom, and in the shape of an electric bass guitar. Both designs will be available in most colours. They may also be repainted as per your wish. \
\
