\pard\tx566\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\pardirnatural

\b0\fs32 \cf0 Navigation in the Phantom Guitar\'ae app is pretty straightforward. Once your on the mode selection page, you can go to any of the modes and press the back button at any time to return to the previous screen, and press it once again to open up a dialog to disconnect the bean and return to the connection screen.\
\
Another important part to be known when using the Phantom Guitar\'ae is the Settings Page. \
\
\pard\tx566\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\pardirnatural

